    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented here is an automotive specimen of the highest caliber, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle reflects a standard of care that transcends the ordinary, offering a driving experience that remains as refined as the day it first left the assembly line. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, has been preserved with exacting precision. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents an unparalleled acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
