    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is in showroom state, featuring supple, uncreased leather that still carries the distinct 'new car' aroma, with zero wear on the seat bolsters or steering wheel. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service binder documenting every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every component functions with precision. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
