      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with proactive rear subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout. Suspension geometry is factory-spec, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for razor-sharp handling. Mechanically overhauled with a recent rod bearing service and valve adjustment. This is a collector-quality example with zero deferred maintenance and a documented service pedigree.",
